---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Socials from "./Socials.astro";
---

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="col">
                <h2 class="title">Around the World in 10 days</h2>
                <p class="text">
                    Travel has always been my way of reconnecting with what
                    truly matters. There’s something powerful about stepping
                    into the unknown — discovering quiet coastal towns, meeting
                    locals with stories to tell, and watching the sun set over
                    landscapes you’ve only seen in photos. Each destination
                    leaves a mark, shaping memories that last far beyond the
                    journey itself.
                </p>
                <p class="text">
                    From early morning walks along palm-lined beaches to
                    spontaneous detours down hidden roads, every day brings a
                    new perspective. It’s not just about ticking places off a
                    list — it’s about immersing yourself in the culture, tasting
                    unfamiliar flavors, and finding beauty in simple, unplanned
                    moments.
                </p>
                <p class="text">
                    Travel reminds us that the world is vast, vibrant, and
                    endlessly inspiring — and that sometimes the best
                    experiences are the ones we never expected.
                </p>
                <Socials />
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <Image
                    class="img-1"
                    src="/images/around-world-1.jpg"
                    width={527}
                    height={351}
                    alt="Brazil beach"
                />
                <Image
                    class="img-2"
                    src="/images/around-world-2.jpg"
                    width={374}
                    height={249}
                    alt="Girl on the road surrounded by palms"
                />
                <Image
                    class="img-comment"
                    src="/images/comment-star.png"
                    width={60}
                    height={49}
                    alt="Comment icon with star inside"
                />
                <p class="caption-text">
                    Travel far enough to meet yourself — somewhere between the
                    waves, the wind, and the wonder of a new place.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section {
        padding: 100px 0 20px;
    }

    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 41% 59%;
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .col {
        &:first-of-type {
            padding: 60px 0 150px;
        }

        &:last-of-type {
            position: relative;
        }
    }

    .title {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .text {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        color: var(--color-dark);
        font-family: var(--family-lora);

        &:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
    }

    .img-1 {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
    }

    .img-2 {
        position: absolute;
        top: 29%;
        left: 10%;
    }

    .img-comment {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20%;
        left: 17%;
    }

    .caption-text {
        position: absolute;
        top: 38%;
        right: 0%;
        max-width: 300px;
        letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-xxs);
        font-size: 44px;
        font-family: var(--family-epic-ride);
    }
</style>
